[div class=p 
	[em 
		"Best of the Best: Championship Karate
	]em
	" is a fighting game that was released for many computer and home console platforms. The home console versions in particular were developed by Loriciel. It is the sequel to 
	[em 
		"Panza Kick Boxing
	]em
	" and features the same gameplay and animations. The objective is to beat various martial artists by depleting their health meter, which is represented by torches. When all of a player's torches go out, the other player wins. This game features a variety of kickboxing moves such as numerous punches and kicks that the player can execute. All of them were carefully rotoscoped to produce fluid and realistic animations of each move.
